snippet.title: Keio Flying Squadron 2 Japanese Ad
snippet.description: A commercial for the second game of one of the most obscure series of all time, the Keio Flying Squadron series. Though the first game (Sega CD) managed to come out in America, the second only got a Japanese and a European release.
